{"tid":1508181,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔醒少少！唔好製造/發佈假新聞！","createTime":"2019-08-26T12:28:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T05:18:08.000Z","uid":139173,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ca28c7fc8264dfee66e0a60bc1cc7e994e537123","tid":1508181,"uid":139173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T12:28:27.000Z","msg":"討論完炒車，FAKE NEWS，暗黑文宣未啊？假既咪冷處理囉，仲推咩啊？<br />\n<br />\n對外，我地已經站穩道德高地，唔需要用假新聞踩底自己。<br />\n<br />\n對內，要拉攏中立派，未經證實既新聞唔該用番啲中性字眼，例如「疑似」，「疑有」。<br />\n<br />\n例如：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">疑有卧底警員喬裝示威者投氣油彈，幸無人受傷</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n有無造假啊？無！講到明疑有，未經証實。但你覺得係咩人做架？卧底警員喬裝示威者。明白中性字眼既威力未啊？如果後尾發現係自己人做咁點啊？冷處理囉，沉底不追究。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>核彈請無限放大大力推，炒車沉底冷處理</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6537ef38e1a1c2c3eb5166f2d9f3481b38191b24","tid":1508181,"uid":35842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T12:29:47.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wjFi3Tp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwjFi3Tp.jpg&h=1a5d1359&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">901 和你塞 13:00 見</span></span> <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsQu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=abe8f3a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\n現有文宣集合 (Google Drive)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsQu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=00b90590\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkY